tagline: Powered by the land governance community
body:
### RFPs

### Documentations

Base documentation of the [Landportal architecture by WESO](http://weso.github.io/landportalDoc/) and the [RDF Data Portal Model](http://weso.github.io/landportalDoc/data/).

### Landportal projects

This a collection of tools and modules used by Landportal to publish and share it's data.

* Model - https://github.com/landportal/model
* Data Access API - https://github.com/landportal/data-access-api
* Importers - https://github.com/landportal/importers
* Receiver - https://github.com/landportal/receiver
* RDF generator - https://github.com/landportal/rdf-generator
* Drupal - https://github.com/landportal/drupal

#### External projects used by Landportal

* [Wesby](https://github.com/weso/Wesby) – “Linked Open Data Viewer”
* [wesCountry](https://github.com/weso/webCountry) – “Visualise data as easy as never before”
